regen.absent_element: notification or alert for case record updates
regen.new_specification: The system shall notify or alert users when case records are updated automatically as the case definition changes.

regen.absent_element: mechanism for handling inconsistent or outdated data in reusable questionnaire libraries
regen.new_specification: The system shall have a mechanism to handle inconsistencies or outdated data in the reusable questionnaire libraries, ensuring data integrity and accuracy during case investigations.

regen.absent_element: notification or alert when case definition changes
regen.new_specification: The system shall notify users of case definition changes and provide an alert when updates to case records are required.
